<p>
  Thanks for signing up to <strong><%= site_name %></strong>,
  <%= name.first %>!
</p>

<p>
  To continue creating your <%= site_name %> account,
  click the link below.
</p>

<%= helpers.button[verify_url, "Verify your account"] %>

<p>
  If the above link does not work, copy and paste the following link into your
  browser:

  <a href="<%= verify_url %>"><%= verify_url %></a>
</p>

<p>
  If you did not request to sign up to <%= site_name %>,
  you can safely ignore this email.
</p>

<p>
  Have a great day!
</p>
